# =============================================================================
# .clinerules - Simula Training Data Framework Specification
# ML Training Data Generation & Governance
# =============================================================================
# This specification defines the Simula framework for generating synthetic
# training data for enterprise AI models with full lineage and governance.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFICATION OVERVIEW
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Purpose

The Simula Training Data Framework specification defines:
- **Data Generation**: Synthetic training data creation patterns
- **Taxonomy Engine**: Hierarchical classification and tagging
- **Quality Assurance**: Data validation and verification
- **Lineage Tracking**: Full provenance from source to model

## Key Documents

| Document | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `simula-training-spec.tex` | Main specification document |
| `chapters/05-taxonomy-engine.tex` | Taxonomy structure and rules |
| `chapters/12-implementation-instructions.tex` | Implementation guidance |
| `references.bib` | Bibliography and citations |

